{"type": "article", "id": 60709, "title": "一批新春广告上架，生化危机 2 也上线了互动广告 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人的一切", "date": "2019-01-28T05:14:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3974, "name": "互动"}, {"id": 15659, "name": "片头"}, {"id": 56264, "name": "美的空调"}, {"id": 55776, "name": "生化危机2"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 1480589, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/20190128120540L6cuwn5oUFRkNaTO.gif", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p line=\"LI5k\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4332724624426028?\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">张艺兴升级成为 Valentino 大中华区男装代言人，</a>并且身着品牌服饰为 2 月份 《GQ 智族》拍摄了拍摄了封面。这之前他是 Valentino 中国区首位品牌大使。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190128120607gcXP5lwLhdEZ4aj8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.374074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190128120608ZFNxogrjapuyt6bG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.343519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190128120609TC6xjH5gA12IMhbk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.343519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"6xGS\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4332076146183908?\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>HOGAN 宣布吴磊成为全新中国区代言人，</b></a>之前是张天爱。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190128120734PnRawb6p3rmJBtOA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一看的 Case</h3><p line=\"DVTO\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUyNzAyMDg1Mw==&amp;mid=2247483913&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1e6ef6b65dd47019ea9cc00584707b79&amp;chksm=fa04a453cd732d4541b38f66bc1bf24e890ef95b5611dbc7a69e006e6220483089a653450882&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0128jdIFPyFOhrEcqjj6MHdF&amp;key=f1dfc5c7113b9346e67373a1e977238985bf0e3c218a725658a5e1f5da87dfc8eee7475f9b75c40fa6005748a0f81c17543557b7e61d0ac49a1b02cd83fb61b8d7cdf0378011b38a973d6b61c34d3d23&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=U%2BaXAirflJ6F4ZVgwXsoACIY%2Bh9Su3f3c7j8mzG7KMlEhZ7WsvYcDVw9kN8vt3So\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>美的为无风感空调制作的“我的爷爷很普通”，</b></a>故事从无所不能的爷爷视角展开，结尾转折这都是来自于爷爷是个游戏玩家，表达年龄不是限定选项的观点。创意代理商来自 Pickle。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=f0819889ixr\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"ymg0\"><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUxNzA4NTQxNQ==&amp;mid=2247486226&amp;idx=3&amp;sn=65815be9d4ae2541b01767a13be2db7e&amp;chksm=f99cca9aceeb438cdacaa082ab883ac58da9740a95b49fa7c284f699a041725048397e41f27c&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0128yJFMrl5OUgcMpuMg6u5C&amp;key=f1dfc5c7113b93469c770d62b9c4a0ac908a08709a81d801bfff862a8bd8a3861e4c7a4c8eb0052b4b7e4005bdeb1611e792dbcecc5987c4c68b1374f2d476eeb80bfa6dbe2c8bdcc7c278d95ca513b5&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=U%2BaXAirflJ6F4ZVgwXsoACIY%2Bh9Su3f3c7j8mzG7KMlEhZ7WsvYcDVw9kN8vt3So\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>京东 7fresh 发布了新春终极新鲜的广告片，</b></a>现在过年更要吃点“新鲜的”。剧情展现了生鲜商品上到餐桌前的心理活动，和之前<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/58240.html\">京东电器</a>的广告相似，文案比较有意思。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=s0830a1si0c\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"x9iO\" class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hd.baomitu.com/ext/bk/\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">360 手机助手联合贝壳租房发布了一支“城市守护人”主题 H5。</a>用户先试听城市里常听又被忽略的噪声，然后告诉参与者这是建筑工人、城市保洁人员和高楼清洁工工作必经的一部分。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190128124017hLkpPHxXSqemgQ8D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190128124032FoQ9lZeLJvz7sEak.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.714667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"x9iO\" class=\"\"><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIzMzY1MDMxOA==&amp;mid=2247484187&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0d0c2c483d3edeec6fa4cf4fe8184c03&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" rel=\"nofollow\">最近制作公司&nbsp;StinkGroup 表示乐事的新春广告创意和自己之前的一支广告太过雷同。</a></b></p><p line=\"x9iO\" class=\"\"><b></b>StinkGroup 在自己的公众号上提到 2016 年与法国导演 Nieto 合作为Argos 制作的品牌广告片，通过把快递过程立体化呈现\"今日下单，今日送达\" 的品牌特点。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=l0827jp6q41\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"x9iO\" class=\"\">乐事的新春广告中同样采用了立体化的呈现方式，甚至广告布景也十分相似，摸狗狗的细节同样转化到了摸小猪上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=k0029mw4r32\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"x9iO\" class=\"\"><a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4331547895535142?\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" rel=\"nofollow\">JINS&nbsp;和豆瓣联合出品的新春广告“活地图老爸”温暖催泪，</a>不服老的父亲在女儿家小住一阵，迷了几次路。即使不再是年轻时候的“活地图”，还是手绘了小区附近的地图。此外，这是张大鹏执导的另一支新春广告片。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=n0830py5qrv\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"x9iO\" class=\"\"><b style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"https://www.thedrum.com/creative-works/project/serviceplan-sky-miss-the-start-miss-the-story\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sky Germany 发布的系列宣传海报，</a></b>把 Kill Bill，Goldfinger，Trainspotting 和 Braveheart 等电影标题的首字母去掉。海报巧妙展示了错过电影开头的痛苦，来推荐用户使用 Sky Q 的重新播放功能。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190128120941PwyTKklfZ1vhAbD3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190128120940W4fbc7ThxZuwr2QL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190128120940LTsjElo76HP3NrSV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20190128120940vOLbl4q8fKwjiGZa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707451\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p line=\"Ivjk\"><b><a href=\"https://youtu.be/erNAkefFjzM\" rel=\"nofollow\">生化危机 2 重置版上周上市之际，在 YouTube 上推出一支剧情先导片。</a></b>片子使用了 YouTube TrueView 互动广告格式，观众选择不同人物和情节和剧情进行互动，深入体验游戏的不同场景。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=g0832jsd3fq\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p line=\"GVNq\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UM-FV0LYU0g\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>亚马逊今年的超级碗广告预告片也发布了。</b></a>Harrison Ford, Forest Whitaker 和 Ilana Glazer 等明星出现在其中，对 Alexa 技术进行测试。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=n083257mvtj\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=z08322zkcyc\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=b0832opdh1b\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/txp/iframe/player.html?vid=t0832uzsjf7\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p line=\"arr2\"><b><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3ODgwNTAzNw==&amp;mid=2659021361&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0c9beefcd631c29332c8637d85ca7d94&amp;chksm=8434f373b3437a65bbaae78dcc58420d09f579fe0ff195c13714f6d7ce03e3f595753399d9da&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0128QghOjnsMwON0CpUtMZh8&amp;key=d1d339c196718166a614557eda53e5b5b925a1e7a9682a4465ab1320d86758c44c2a2ea625dc4a980376fffc739941c61fe8659a4304b190863c189998eb9cefcf82e0009042419c38071af07f07522d&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MjgzNjA1MjcyMQ%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir7%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.14+build(18A391)&amp;version=12020010&amp;nettype=WIFI&amp;lang=en&amp;fontScale=100&amp;pass_ticket=U%2BaXAirflJ6F4ZVgwXsoACIY%2Bh9Su3f3c7j8mzG7KMlEhZ7WsvYcDVw9kN8vt3So\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">微信公布了 </a><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3ODgwNTAzNw==&amp;mid=2659021361&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0c9beefcd631c29332c8637d85ca7d94&amp;chksm=8434f373b3437a65bbaae78dcc58420d09f579fe0ff195c13714f6d7ce03e3f595753399d9da&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=0128QghOjnsMwON0CpUtMZh8&amp;key=d1d339c196718166a614557eda53e5b5b925a1e7a9682a4465ab1320d86758c44c2a2ea625dc4a980376fffc739941c61fe8659a4304b190863c189998eb9cefcf82e0009042419c38071af07